{"tid":2217079,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍被打爆痱滋案 裝修工暴動等罪共判囚4年","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T07:55:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d3a3d03689528a2462fd67fc2789cb11a6a4a4","tid":2217079,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"包圍警總警員被打爆痱滋案 裝修工暴動等罪共判囚4年<br />\n<br />\n去年6月26日包圍警察總部案，警員供稱受襲致痱滋爆裂，26歲被告裝修工人岑曉麟上星期四被裁定暴動罪及普通襲擊罪成，他早前又承認一項無合理因由而沒有按照法庭的指定歸押，今日在區域法院被判囚4年。<br />\n<br />\n法官上周裁決時表示，警員遇襲痱滋爆裂實屬十分輕微，甚至可以說是微不足道，控方原本提出檢控被告襲擊引致他人身體受傷罪，不符客觀證據。<br />\n<br />\n法官又提到，不得不承認處理本案案情有困難，因涉及暴動行為與以往案例有別，不是一般與警方對抗、掟磚、襲警等行為，或在同類案件中算是輕微，判刑需作多方面平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551612-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551612-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzs5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=a03e0302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551612-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=624f4ca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551612-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"95e296c59812cde7c004ea6a1d3a244b43051e78","tid":2217079,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a26880500b653dc07e559b262ba0087bde76a83","tid":2217079,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"痴撚線咁都4年屌你老母"},{"pid":"dc088f8ace23656eb1b952f01cfd068a53aa7803","tid":2217079,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"4年一係蘇文隆<br />\n一係胡雅文"},{"pid":"750977d178608d46dfdb15fbb79c64fc742b7f4b","tid":2217079,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"痴撚線屌你老母<img src=